function serverLocation(hn){const h=String(hn||'').toLowerCase();const cities={'ams':t('cityAms'),'fra':t('cityFra'),'waw':t('cityWaw'),'lon':t('cityLon'),'hel':t('cityHel'),'sto':t('citySto')};const flags={'ams':String.fromCodePoint(127475,127473),'fra':String.fromCodePoint(127465,127466),'waw':String.fromCodePoint(127477,127473),'lon':String.fromCodePoint(127468,127463),'hel':String.fromCodePoint(127467,127470),'sto':String.fromCodePoint(127480,127466)};for(const[pre]of Object.entries(cities)){if(h.startsWith(pre)){const name=hn.slice(pre.length).replace(/^[-_\s]+/,'');return flags[pre]+' '+cities[pre]+' ('+esc(name||hn)+')'}}return '🌍 '+esc(hn)}
